Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be6\blur2.25}罩著披風看不出拿的啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be6\blur2.25}披風？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be6\blur2.25}嗯啊
